rows.label: qst101107_msg0001
rows.name:
You've come a long way to
this remote place, mo.

rows.label: qst101107_msg0002
rows.name: Buying something, mo?

rows.label: qst101107_msg0003
rows.name:
You're here on Yorgo-ossan's behalf,
mo? Ah, for the Gulan Walnut, mo.

rows.label: qst101107_msg0004
rows.name:
I'll sell you Gulan Walnut
for 10,000G a piece, mo.

rows.label: qst101107_msg0005
rows.name:
I have an order for three,
so... if you have 30,000G,
your errand is done, mo.

rows.label: qst101107_msg0006
rows.name:
Surprised it's more expensive than
usual, mo? Can't be helped, mo.

rows.label: qst101107_msg0007
rows.name:
Gulan Walnut grows with the
blessing of the Divine Beast, mo.

rows.label: qst101107_msg0008
rows.name:
Recently, more Divine Beasts
have been weakening, mo?
Gula is no exception, mo.

rows.label: qst101107_msg0009
rows.name:
The Gulan Walnuts that can be used
for lumber aren't growing well, mo.

rows.label: qst101107_msg0010
rows.name:
They're starting to become rare,
so the price is going up, mo.

rows.label: qst101107_msg0011
rows.name:
If you don't have the
money, I'll trade you for
some Muscle Branch, mo.

rows.label: qst101107_msg0012
rows.name:
It's hard for Nopon to gather,
so it's valuable, mo.

rows.label: qst101107_msg0040
rows.name:
What will you do, mo? Pay with
money, mo? Or trade for goods, mo?

rows.label: qst101107_msg0052
rows.name: What will you do?

rows.label: qst101107_msg0050
rows.name: Pay with gold

rows.label: qst101107_msg0051
rows.name: Trade goods

rows.label: qst101107_msg0060
rows.name: Come again, mo.

rows.label: qst101107_msg0101
rows.name:
Yorgo ordered three Gulan Walnuts,
mo. I still have some left, mo.

rows.label: qst101107_msg0201
rows.name: The Gulan Walnut is sold out, mo.

rows.label: qst101107_msg0202
rows.name:
If the Divine Beast doesn't
recover, we won't be able
to get any more, mo.

rows.label: qst101107_msg0203
rows.name:
Business is getting tough,
mo... I might have to move
to another Divine Beast, mo.
